                <doc>Each bit corresponds to the request opcode enum.
If a bit is set, request to High Bandwidth MI-P will be directed to
EID = direct_eid (as configured in the relevant sam region).
If a bit is 0, request to High Bandwidth MI-P will be directed
to EID = (direct_eid + 1)
The bitmap[reg_index][bitmap_j] corresponds to 32 * reg_index + bitmap_j</doc>
                <sw>rw</sw>
                <hw>ro</hw>
                <default unresolvedDef="0">00000000000000000000000000000000</default>
            </field>
